swipe through for a short interview from @rebel.mag with the homie @clarecirillo . arguably one of the best feelings to come from what i do are the often unexpected relationships that develop out of happenstance life moments. i met clare while shooting at another dear friend's restaurant, and from jump our friendship has felt effortless and honest. my overthinking self often wonders, what is it that makes me click with some people and not with others? with clare, it's a shared sense of safe space. heart on sleeve wearing energy that desires to express it all and find connection while doing so. this shoot was special cause we got to explore her childhood and where she grew up, while also processing some things we've both been working through as adults trying to keep a strong connection to our inner child. grateful to count clare among my dear homies who i feel free to just *be* around, including the whole spectrum of becoming that being entails

#allaboutrelationship
